<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>١ - <span class="c1">"تاريخ ابن مَعِين"</span> <span class="c2">(٢/ ٥٠٧)</span> وقال: <span class="c1">"ليس بشيء"</span>.<span class="c5"> وقال مَرَّةً:</span> <span class="c1">"صالح الحديث"</span>.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>٢ - <span class="c1">"التاريخ الكبير"</span> <span class="c2">(١/ ٥٠)</span> وقال: <span class="c1">"فيه نظر"</span>.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>٣ - <span class="c1">"الضعفاء"</span> للنَّسَائي ص ٢١٣ رقم <span class="c2">(٥٤٥)</span> وقال: <span class="c1">"ضعيف"</span>.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>